<p>The lead quality data is equally strong. SEO leads close at 14.6%, compared to just 1.7% for outbound marketing, according to SmartBug Media research from 2026. Local SEO leads are actively searching for your service. They are not cold prospects. They are warm leads with demonstrated intent.</p>
